# Worksheet context

Copy this file to `rules/context.md` (gitignored) and fill in your values.

## Identity

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| Name | Your Full Name |
| Email | your@email.com |

## Companies

| Role | Company |
|---|---|
| Employer | Your employer |
| Client | Your client |

## Contacts

| Name | Role | Email |
|---|---|---|
| Admin contact name | Administration | admin@company.com |

## Locations

| Name | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| City A | Client office | on-site days |
| City B | Client office | on-site days |
| City C | Meetup location | matches `City C-Meetup` calendar event |

## Your Company project codes

| Project | Code |
|---|---|
| Default (client on-site / remote) | Client-YourName |
| Meetup | Meetup |
| Leave / Sick | Verlof / Leave |
| Vacation | Vakantie / Vacation |
| National Holiday | Feestdag / National Holiday |

